item.dc:creator: @gunztheduel gunztheduel
item.description:
@gunztheduel wrote:

Most tutorials tell you to paste voids. A void starts with stuff like -

public void TankedJare()

They end in }

Then another void would come next. You have to paste your void between the voids.
